data.description: Historic home on the Washington Blvd! Original hardwood floors and woodwork throughout. Large windows bring in natural light to shine on the character of this beautiful home. Spacious 5 bedrooms with walk in closets. Country charm kitchen with exposed brick chimney and built in pantry. Large living room with a cozy fireplace. Three updated bathrooms and a built in vanity. Dining room with an original swinging door into the kitchen. Full finished basement with outside access. Outside we have a peaceful front porch with a swing that overlooks the beautiful mature trees on the Boulevard and Washington's only brick road. Large oversized updated 2 car garage complete with a indoor/outdoor chicken pen and work bench. The backyard is fenced in with an above ground salt water pool. All services to the home are under ground. Built in security system and Ring doorbell cameras. The home is conveniently located within walking distance of the Sunset Park and Washington's historic downtown square. One seller is a licensed Realtor in the state of Iowa.
